d comparison to MHD simulations\nof star formation processes in filamentary structures of molecular clouds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Jul 2020 16:52:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Jul 2020 18:10:15 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 28 Dec 2020 05:25:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-24"}
